!! Prefixes
!  --------
!! Prefixes in the Purubora language are attatched to the left of other words.

LEXICON Prefixes
verbprefix-     Verbs   ;

! All nouns will have a preceding choice between prefix or not
@U.PN.SG1@:@U.PN.SG1@o%< Nouns ;!this one gets tagged afterwards
@U.PN.SG2@:@U.PN.SG2@e%< Nouns ;!this one gets tagged afterwards
@U.PN.SG3@:@U.PN.SG3@a%< Nouns ;!this one gets tagged afterwards
     Nouns   ;!this one will not be tagged

! vim: set ft=xfst-lexc:
